  "id": "RAW_c8790646",
  "title": "Claude 这个更新，让模型能力提升 10%+！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTA1OTAxNA==&mid=2247488868&idx=1&sn=1f606c49161ba0619eeb2bebb1a4a24b",
  "date": "2026-03-15 04:08:00",
  "author": "花叔",
  "siteName": "花叔",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;\">大多数人低估了昨天 Claude开放 100 万上下文长度的更新，从 200K 到 1M，上下文长度其实不是提升到原来的 5 倍，而是 7 倍、8 倍、9 倍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为原来 200K 的上下文里有很大一部分会被系统提示词、记忆、skills，以及预留的 compact buffer 所占据。所以你真正可使用的项目上下文长度其实就 100K 出头，现在在 1M 上下文里，项目可用的上下文提升到了 900K 左右。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 6px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我打开 /context 截了两张图：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);margin: 6px 0px 4px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Sonnet 4.6（200K）——打开对话就用掉了 25%</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100005212\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4981481481481482\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232);font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:block;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;width:660px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7e638c5b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSWibwcunCiaib4pUMDEogpqdUoemTuKWBNlmCDCSrpX2RbriaKLe9LGDDgbiceLbt5O3cBOSDlVYoN1Uh52jCtRR7ToEPssMWrVlCCxs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);margin: 6px 0px 4px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Opus 4.6（1M）——同样的 skill 配置，用掉的比例缩到 4%</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100005213\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232);font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:block;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;width:660px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f936b45c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSWibregVSWeDw3wtPglv9ajgF8hY2zuJdbjMhmQSrotVOl9QKR3P1A3mNxDcDFSQ78SLgErMiamDRayYgr8ZhHcfCNsmUGXq2dhqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:14px 18px;margin:20px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(227, 18, 11);font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">Free space 的对比：</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 4px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\">· Sonnet 4.6（200K）：free space&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">118k</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（58.8%）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\">· Opus 4.6（1M）：free space&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">923k</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（92.3%）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\">923 ÷ 118 ≈&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">7.8 倍</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。名义上 5 倍，实际可用空间接近 8 倍。对于 skill 配置越重的用户，这个数字越夸张——这就是我说它等效于 6-10 倍的原因。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:14px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">被 compact 折磨过的人都懂这是什么感觉。对话太长触发 compact，有时候顺，有时候直接失败，对话就卡死了。重开，手动粘贴上下文，每次都有信息损耗，然后模型在同一个地方再犯一遍你以为解决了的错。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.3;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">上下文不是容量，是草稿纸</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">费曼不相信自己说不清楚的东西。他的标准是：把所有符号去掉还能讲清楚，才算真理解。上下文限制限制的不只是能放进去多少内容。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:12px 0px 12px 20px;margin:20px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(227, 18, 11);font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:0px;font-weight:700;font-size:19px;line-height:1.5;font-style:italic;\"><span leaf=\"\">你正在解一道复杂的数学题，做到一半，我把你的草稿纸拿走了。你变笨了吗？没有。但你能解出那道题吗？也不能了。</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">问题出在草稿纸，不在你的大脑。模型的上下文就是它的草稿纸。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">记忆不只是存储，是推理的原材料。推导结论，前提和中间步骤得记在某个地方，才能一步步往下走。每推一步就忘一步，算力再猛也推不出来。上下文窗口就是模型的有效记忆范围，超出去只能猜。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 6px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以模型出错很多时候不是不够聪明，是看不见：</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232);font-variant-caps:normal;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">代码开发：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">bug 的根源在三个文件之前引入的变量定义。那个定义超出上下文了，模型看不见，只能猜。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">长文写作：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">写到后半段，前面某个论点超出窗口了。模型开始隐隐复述已经说过的东西，或者前后逻辑出现细微矛盾。你改稿时才发现，时间没了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">多轮对话：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">第 3 轮定的约束到第 30 轮消失了。建议越来越奇怪，你说不出哪里不对，就是感觉「它没在听」。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">上下文越小，这类残缺越多，判断越差。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.3;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据：上下文越长，Claude 和其他模型差距越大</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据也能说明这件事。Anthropic 用 MRCR v2（8-needle）测了一组长上下文检索，任务是在超长文本里同时找多个藏起来的关键信息。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9138888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border:1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232);font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:block;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;width:660px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-imgfileid=\"100005214\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7ade8398&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSW8CYtuTx4nHQb1dOqNmibibheBUeXo0hKdeDViaia9GI6C6R9o0cFEynvDKrqMnlj9vWnOm0CgtPzFaQK9GNgiarx4CicvicSBlNMG94c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <table style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;width:660px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;\">\n   <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(29, 29, 27);\">\n     <th style=\"text-align: left;padding: 8px 10px;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">模型</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"text-align: center;padding: 8px 10px;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">256K</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"text-align: center;padding: 8px 10px;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">1M</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);\">\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Claude Opus 4.6</span></strong></td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">91.9%</span></strong></td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">78.3%</span></strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);\">\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Claude Sonnet 4.6</span></strong></td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">90.6%</span></strong></td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">65.1%</span></strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);\">\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">GPT-5.4</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">79.3%†</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">36.6%</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);\">\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3.1 Pro</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">59.1%</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"text-align: center;padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">25.9%</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);margin: -8px 0px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">† GPT-5.4 的 256K 数据为 128K–256K 区间均值</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:14px 16px;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(227, 18, 11);font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">上下文越长，差距越大。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;256K 时几个模型还挤在一起，拉到 1M，GPT-5.4 掉到 36.6%，Gemini 3.1 Pro 掉到 25.9%，Claude Opus 4.6 还在 78.3%。不是 Claude 在短上下文里更强——是拉长之后别人扛不住，Claude 还在。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:14px 0px 6px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 的 PM Boris Cherny 也在推上确认了一件事：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.7;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Opus 4.6 1M 现在是 Claude Code&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Max、Team、Enterprise</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;的默认模型，不用改任何设置。Pro 版和 Sonnet 用&nbsp;</span></span><code style=\"border-radius:3px;padding:1px 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">/extra-usage</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;手动开启。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 还引用了个客户案例：用上 1M 上下文之后，自动压缩事件减少了 15%。这跟我自己的体感对得上。我自己估，对长期迭代的复杂项目，这个价值至少等于模型能力提升 10%-20%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.3;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">API也取消溢价了</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">900K token 的请求和 9K token，现在一个价：</span></p>\n  <table style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;width:660px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;\">\n   <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(29, 29, 27);\">\n     <th style=\"text-align: left;padding: 8px 10px;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">服务商</span></p>\n     </th>\n     <th style=\"text-align: left;padding: 8px 10px;font-size: 11px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">长上下文怎么收费</span></p>\n     </th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);\">\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic Claude</span></strong></td>\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 18, 11);\"><span leaf=\"\">✓ 无溢价，和短上下文一个价</span></strong></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);\">\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI GPT-5.4</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"padding: 9px 10px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">超过 272K 输入收 2× 单价，输出 1.5×</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 收长度税，Anthropic 现在不收了。终于，上下文成了top模型的标配。理论上长上下文也确实不该是高级功能，本身就该是个模型基础能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code Max 用户（100 刀/月那档）更简单，1M 上下文直接就有，不用加参数，不用多付钱。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.3;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">顺带还有两件事</span></p>\n  <table style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:16px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;width:660px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:start;\">\n   <tbody>\n    <tr>\n     <td style=\"padding: 14px;border: 1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);vertical-align: top;\">\n      <p style=\"font-size: 11px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px 0px 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更新&nbsp;<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mmr88pdd-unuyss\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#1</a></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">图片 / PDF 上限 100 → 600</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前一堆 PDF 要手动拆批，现在一次喂进去。我每次写文章要整理十几张截图和参考资料，这个直接省了好几步。</span></p>\n     </td>\n     <td style=\"padding: 14px;border: 1px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);vertical-align: top;\">\n      <p style=\"font-size: 11px;color: rgb(97, 97, 97);letter-spacing: 0.8px;margin: 0px 0px 6px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更新&nbsp;<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mmr88pdd-jpihjv\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#2</a></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Adaptive Thinking 转正式版</span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型自己判断什么时候慢想、什么时候直接答，不用你手动配置推理深度。少了一层不必要的决策。</span></p>\n     </td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:19px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.3;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Context，Not Control.</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 工具的进步有两种：模型变聪明，或者把已有的能力真正释放出来。1M 上下文 GA 是后者。但对于长期项目、复杂开发、以及被 compact 搞崩过的人，实际影响不比前者小。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">费曼说过，背下来一个公式，和能自己从头推导出来，是两回事，重量完全不同。给模型喂答案，和给它喂能推导出答案的所有信息，也是两回事。后者更难，但结果更靠谱。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">上下文窗口，决定了你能给它多少推导所需的信息。之前太小，你得做减法——剪掉那些「可能有用但放不进去」的东西。每次剪，都是在赌这段信息不重要。赌对了没感觉，赌错了，模型就在某个你看不见的地方犯了一个你找不出原因的错。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在，你完全可以肆无忌惮去给模型投喂任何你觉得它该知道的信息了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 14px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">👇这个管理理念不止是在Netflix和字节，在大模型的使用和管理上也越来越有效了</span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:12px 0px 12px 20px;margin:20px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(227, 18, 11);font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:0px;font-weight:700;font-size:19px;line-height:1.5;font-style:italic;\"><span leaf=\"\">Context，Not Control.</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度解析了 Claude 1M 上下文更新的实际价值，指出其可用空间提升接近 8 倍，并在长文本检索性能和计费策略上显著领先竞品。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度解析了 Claude 1M 上下文更新的实际价值，指出其可用空间提升接近 8 倍，并在长文本检索性能和计费策略上显著领先竞品。",
  "summary": "文章针对 Anthropic 最近将 Claude 上下文长度从 200K 提升至 1M 的更新进行了专业解读。作者指出，由于系统提示词、技能配置和压缩缓冲区等固定开销的存在，名义上的 5 倍提升在实际使用中（特别是重度用户）等效于 8 倍左右的可用空间增量。文章通过 MRCR v2 检索测试数据对比了 Claude Opus 4.6 与 GPT-5.4、Gemini 3.1 Pro 在长上下文下的表现，强调了 Claude 在极长文本下的准确率优势。此外，文章还提到了 Anthropic 取消了长上下文的溢价收费、增加了图片/PDF 上传上限至 600 个，以及正式发布 Adaptive Thinking 功能。作者认为，长上下文不仅是容量的增加，更是模型推理“草稿纸”的质变，能显著减少复杂项目中的逻辑断层和错误。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "1M 上下文的实际可用空间提升远超名义上的 5 倍，接近 8 倍。",
      "explanation": "因为系统提示词和技能配置等固定开销在 200K 窗口中占比极高（约 25%），而在 1M 窗口中占比仅约 4%，使得实际留给用户的自由空间从 118K 跃升至 923K。"
    },
    {
      "point": "上下文窗口是模型的“草稿纸”，直接影响复杂任务的推理质量。",
      "explanation": "模型出错往往是因为关键信息超出了上下文窗口导致“看不见”。长上下文能为代码开发、长文写作和多轮对话提供完整的推理原材料，减少因信息损耗导致的幻觉。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在 1M 长度下，Claude 的检索准确率显著优于 GPT 和 Gemini 等竞品。",
      "explanation": "MRCR v2 测试显示，在 1M 上下文时，Opus 4.6 的准确率仍保持在 78.3%，而 GPT-5.4 和 Gemini 3.1 Pro 分别掉至 36.6% 和 25.9%，体现了极强的长程关联能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Anthropic 采取了无溢价的计费策略，推动长上下文成为模型标配。",
      "explanation": "不同于 OpenAI 对长输入收取双倍单价的“长度税”，Claude 的长短上下文输入价格一致，降低了用户处理超大规模数据集的成本门槛。"
    }
